all stats of player (https://api.opendota.com/api/players/{account_id})

wl(all)(https://api.opendota.com/api/players/{account_id}/wl)

stats for matches(https://api.opendota.com/api/players/{account_id}/matches)

stats for last match(https://api.opendota.com/api/players/ID_OF_PLAYER/rec..)(всегда выводить первым id_of_player)

stats for hero(all)(https://api.opendota.com/api/players/{account_id}/heroes)

stats with friend(https://api.opendota.com/api/players/1084744980/peers)

stats of the last spoken word
(https://api.opendota.com/api/players/1084744980/wordc..)(можно сделать с героями) РАБОТАЕТ ОЧЕНЬ СТРАННО!

stats for team(https://api.opendota.com/api/teams/ID_OF_TEAM)

stats for all players of team (https://api.opendota.com/api/teams/ID_OF_TEAM/players)(добавить отсечение бывших участников)

stats for all heroes of team
(https://api.opendota.com/api/teams/ID_OF_TEAM/heroes)